We recommended that Management:

1.	Continue appropriating GAD Funds of not less than 5% of the total budget and submit the GAD Plan and Budget for review of the DILG on time;




2.	Execute those plans accordingly in order to achieve the desired results;




3.	Instruct the lead person/responsible office to implement the GAD Plan accordingly in order to fully achieve the performance target indicated in the GAD Plan; and

4.	Maximize the utilization of GAD Budget to pursue women’s empowerment and gender equality.
